{"tid":2441926,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲歡迎許智峯在當地展開游說： 他享有言論及政治活動自由","createTime":"2021-03-11T04:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T04:26:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf816363da1d351e4e029b8151b66290506cccf1","tid":2441926,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"前立法會議員許智峯周二由英國轉往澳洲，是當地封關下首個成功入境的非澳洲公民。澳洲國會情報及安全委員會帕特森（James Paterson）表示，歡迎他在澳洲展開游說行動，稱他享有言論及政治活動自由。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月經丹麥流亡到英國後，許智峯再轉抵澳洲繼續其國際游說工作。受武漢肺炎疫情影響，澳洲一直封關禁止非公民入境，帕特森回應指入境政策是「純粹的澳洲國內主權問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210311/CNHBMWRFMZADVBJAQTVHX5PO64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210311%2FCNHBMWRFMZADVBJAQTVHX5PO64%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=8a0da94a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210311%2FCNHBMWRFMZADVBJAQTVHX5PO64%2F&h=c48c33d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210311/CNHBMWRFMZADVBJAQTVHX5PO64/</a>"}]}